Class AnimationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.mdx.xmf.swt.diagram.zoom.AnimationModel

  • public class AnimationModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the count information, and notifies interested figures of changes in animation. Created by a root, which loops through the animation process.
